    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>cucumber[s]</strong> in half and slice into half disks</p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Roll your<strong> lime[s]</strong> with your hand on a hard surface (to release more juice!) and cut in half</p>",
