    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> (don't like raw garlic? Go easy!), <strong>mustard seeds</strong> and a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> in a large bowl</p><p>Juice the <strong>lime</strong> into the bowl and season with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> - this is your<strong> lime & mustard seed dressing</strong></p>",
