    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is cooked, remove the pan from the heat and shred the <strong>chicken </strong>apart in the pan, using two forks - this technique is known as ‘pulling’</p><p>Once pulled, add your <strong>Greek-style yoghurt </strong>and <strong>mango chutney</strong> to the pan and give everything a good mix up - this is your <strong>Coronation chicken</strong></p>",
